海外确诊病例数字的攀升幅度已经大大超过中国国内，今天开始，数说疫情开始把重点转向全球的疫情发展文 |《财经》数据研究员徐进 图 |《财经》视觉中心 编辑 | 谢丽容 郝洲一、累计确诊病例：全国总病例数有望控制在81000例左右国内3月1日报告累计病例80026例，新增202例。
The number of confirmed cases from overseas has surged far beyond that of China, and today the epidemic is starting to shift its focus to global epidemic development. Caijing Data Researcher Xu Jin-tou and Cherry Ronghao.
新增病例193例来自武汉，广大非武汉地区仅9例。
The 193 new cases came from Wuhan, and only 9 cases were found in non-Wuhan areas.
武汉在300-500区间持续拉锯战终于显露结束迹象。
Wuhan at the 300-500 interval in the continuous tug-of-war finally showed signs of ending.
新增密切接触者人数和新增疑似病例等数据也支持这一判断。
Data such as the number of new close contacts and new suspected cases also support this judgement.
预计全国累计病例数最终会在81000例左右。
The cumulative number of cases nationwide is expected to eventually be around 81,000.
二、海外新增病例加速增长，全球大流行越来越难以避免图1海外的确诊病例持续以每日超过千例的速度在增加，总数逼近10000大关。
With the number of new cases increasing rapidly overseas, it is becoming increasingly difficult to avoid a global pandemic. Figure 1 The number of confirmed cases overseas continues to increase at a rate of over 1,000 per day, reaching a total of nearly 10,000.
而且，全球仍然缺乏统一协调的应对行动，基本上都是各自为战，有个好消息是考虑到伊朗的疫情较为严重且药品短缺，美国已经临时放松了对伊朗采购药品的制裁。
Moreover, the global response remains fragmented, and the good news is that the US has temporarily eased sanctions on Iranian drug purchases, given the severity of the Iranian epidemic and the shortage of medicines.
另外， 中国在国内与疫情相关的医疗物资紧缺的情况下，仍然向韩国、日本等国伸出了援手，“山川异域，风月同天”的故事还在继续上演。
In addition, despite the shortage of medical supplies related to the epidemic in China, China still offers assistance to countries such as South Korea and Japan.
图2全球新增病例按地区分布图在中国以外，疫情扩散主要集中在西太平洋（韩国）、欧洲（意大利、德国、法国和西班牙）和东地中海地区（伊朗），以上地区的确诊总数占海外总确诊人数的90%以上。
Figure 2 Global distribution of new cases by region Outside China, the spread of the epidemic is concentrated in the Western Pacific (Republic of Korea), Europe (Italy, Germany, France and Spain) and the Eastern Mediterranean (Iran), which together account for more than 90 per cent of the total number of confirmed cases overseas.
三、韩国的新增势头仍然难以遏制，确诊人数仍未见顶图3图4（韩国的分区地图）韩国新增数字较快的原因是“新天地”教会成员（总数约为21.5万）在陆续接受病毒检测。
Figures 3 and 4 (South Korea's zoning map) South Korea's new figures are faster because members of the New World Church, totalling about 215,000, are being tested for the virus.
新增病例仍然主要集中在大邱市，占韩国新增总数的74.78%，确诊总数占韩国国内病例总数的73.15%。
New cases remain concentrated in Daegu, accounting for 74.78 per cent of the total number of new cases in South Korea and 73.15 per cent of the total number of cases diagnosed in the country.
在“新天地”教会会长李万熙的家乡庆尚北道，新增占比为15.89%，确诊总数占比为14.81%。
Gyeongshan North Province, the hometown of Li Wanxi, the head of Xintiandi Church, added 15.89 percent, making up 14.81 percent of the total number of diagnoses.
除去这两个“毒源”之外，韩国其他地区还未见大规模扩散。
Apart from these two sources, the rest of South Korea has yet to see large-scale proliferation.
【特别说明：上述统计数据，2月28日前为世卫组织官方统计数据，数据截止时间为北京时间每日17时；从2月28日开始，数据由《财经》根据公开资料统计，截止时间为北京时间每日9时】四、全球疫情数字速览1、【1314名国人回家】外交部领事司司长崔爱民介绍，自疫情发生以来，中国先后派出10架次的航班前往多个国家，接回了1314名中国公民。
2007-9-25 21: 23 [special note: above statistics, February 28 is the official statistics of WHO, the cut-off time is 17: 00 daily Beijing time; from February 28, the deadline is 9: 00am Beijing time.
同时，还积极协助特区政府，从日本接回了钻石公主号上的近200名港澳特区居民。
At the same time, the SAR Government has been actively assisting the SAR Government to retrieve nearly 200 Hong Kong and Macao SAR residents from Japan.
2、【告发13人】韩国时间3月1日晚，首尔市政府向首尔中央检察院递交了对新天地教会会长李万熙及12个支派的会长（共13人）的告发书。
Seoul city government handed over a complaint to Seoul's central procuratorate against Lee Wanxi, president of Xintiandi Church, and 13 presidents of 12 tribes.
3、【30万支排查小组】伊朗卫生部部长纳马基3月1日表示，将成立30万支排查小组来进行抗击疫情计划。
2007-9-24 15: 23 [hide] Health Minister Manouchehr al-Namaki said on March 1 that 300,000 screening teams would be set up to carry out the anti-epidemic plan.
此外，伊朗预算与计划组织向伊朗卫生部拨款2万亿里亚尔(超过1400万美元)，用做抗击新冠肺炎疫情的专门款项。
In addition, the Iranian Budget and Planning Organization allocated 2 trillion riyals (more than $14 million) to the Iranian Ministry of Health for a special allocation to combat the outbreak of pneumonia in the New Crown.
4、【1500万美元应急基金】联合国中央应急基金拨出1500万美元，用于全球特别是医疗保健系统薄弱国家遏制新冠病毒扩散的努力。
4. [$15 million Emergency Response Fund] The United Nations Central Emergency Response Fund has allocated $15 million to global efforts to curb the spread of the cap virus, especially in countries with weak health-care systems.
小结：在全球疫情呈加速状态扩散的情况下，各个国家之间缺乏统一协调行动。
Summary: Given the accelerating spread of the global epidemic, there is a lack of integrated and coordinated action across countries.
世卫组织和全球传染病专家一再警告的全球防疫薄弱环节一旦被突破，将很有可能成为那“最后一根稻草”。
A breakthrough in global epidemic vulnerability, as repeatedly warned by WHO and global infectious disease experts, could well be the "last straw."
武汉拉锯战即将终结，值得庆幸。
Wuhan is about to end the tug-of-war, is fortunate.
